window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The entire world is on the brink of finding out nightmares are real. </p> <p>An army of demons known as the Noctis is growing in strength. They control all manner of foul beasts and if not stopped soon, cities will burn, lives will end, and hope will be lost. </p> <p>The only thing standing in the way are the Journeymen; humans and supernatural beings united against the darkness. </p> <p>There is one known amongst men and the supernatural alike that you don't mess with. Unless it's on his terms. </p> <p>His name is Gage Crosse and he's the best damn Journeyman around. </p> <p>These are his adventures. </p>";